data.description: Home is in pre-foreclosure(NOT SHORT SALE) and is part of an estate sale (NOT PROBATE) with Trustee's Sale scheduled for 12/06/2023. Home has to be in contract no later than 11/30/23. Stunning home in the active adult Trilogy at Vistancia! Nestled on a golf course lot of a cul-de-sac, it is meticulously crafted for a truly unparalleled living experience. A well-manicured landscape and a split 3-car garage w/extended driveway are just the beginning. Discover an excellent floor plan showcasing a formal dining room and a spacious living/family room with a fireplace & surround sound. Adjoining is the cozy nook with a bow window! Neutral palette and tile flooring in all the right places create an appealing interior ambiance filled with abundant natural light. The impeccable kitchen boasts gran Enter the main bedroom to find a bay window, backyard access, and an ensuite with dual sinks & a walk-in closet. One secondary bedroom has its attached full bathroom. Laundry room with sink & cabinetry. You'll love the backyard, offering a covered patio w/built-in BBQ! Here, you can enjoy the panoramic view of the golf course & serene lake, making this outdoor space a private paradise. Let's not forget the fantastic Community amenities! Experience the golf course, clubhouse, fitness center, pools, walking trails, sports courts, and social activities in this vibrant 55+ community. Don't miss this opportunity!
